column2: SELECT TOP #  p.petroMag_g,p.petroMag_r,p.petroMag_u,p.petroMagErr_g,p.petroMagErr_r,p.petroMagErr_u,ISNULL(s.z,#) as redshift,ISNULL(s.zErr,#) as redshiftErr  FROM ..Galaxy AS p  LEFT OUTER JOIN ..SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID  WHERE p.petroMag_u > # AND p.petroMag_g > # AND p.petroMag_r > #
